Package: maIHB
Type: Package
Title: Inference the Maternal Allele Inheritance via Bayesian Approach
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Chunxuan Shao <c.shao@dkfz.de>
Maintainer: Chunxuan Shao <c.shao@dkfz.de>
Description: Inference maternal allele inheritance in fetus in 
  noninvasive prenatal diagnosis via hierarchical Bayesian 
  approach. It uses counts data of SNPs on both maternal Haplotype
  flanking interested genes. Posterior distribution and various 
  diagnosis plots for MCMC simulations are provided.
License: GPL-3
LazyData: TRUE
Imports: BEST,
    coda,
    gtools,
    parallel,
    runjags
